These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, cooking, hiking, gardening
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, d&b, pop, r&b
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, amber, blood-red, fuchsia
There are 4 different nationalities: german, mexican, dutch, brazilian
 1. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the mexican##3
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is the fan of r&b##1
 3. the german is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the dutch is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 5. the german is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 9. the german is on the far left##1
10. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
11. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Hobby    | hiking   | cooking       | puzzles | gardening   |
| Music-Genre        | d&b    | r&b  | pop      | funk |
| Color         | fuchsia      | amber | blood-red         | apricot   |
| Nationality   | german | mexican       | dutch        | brazilian   |

