.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-2::.
House: wooden, cottage, craftsman, tower
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, classical, house, funk
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, drawing, chess, gardening
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, march, may, january
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the cottage house is the fan of reggae##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is the craftsman house##1
4. the wooden house is between the fan of classical and the person who's birthday is in october##2
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person who's birthday is in january##1
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left or far right##3
9. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |       3        |      4       |
| House           | cottage | wooden | tower | craftsman |
| Music-Genre   | reggae  | house | classical         | funk      |
| Hobby         | chess      | drawing    | gardening         | rock-climbing   |
| Birthday     | october         | march    | january          | may         |

