 4. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3
 5. the person eating apricot is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 6. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 7. the person eating orange is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 8. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 9. the person who growsiris is the owner of the cat##1
10. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
11. the havana-smoker is the person eating orange##1

