.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, pony, chinchilla, turtle
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, disco, house, ambient
4 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, bridge, billiard
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, video-games, card-games, cooking
 1. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 4. the fan of disco is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
 5. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
 6. the person playing backgammon is between the fan of disco and the person who's hobby is baking##2
 7. the person playing bridge is the fan of ambient##1
 8. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is the fan of disco##1
10. the person playing backgammon is the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Pet          | pony | turtle   | chinchilla   | fish |
| Music-Genre           | metal   | house     | disco   | ambient |
| Game   | scrabble    | backgammon    | billiard   | bridge   |
| Hobby         | baking    | video-games | cooking | card-games    |

 